{{PIE root|en|mey}}
From {{etyl|enm|en}} {{m|en|ministre}}, from {{etyl|fro|en}} {{m|en|ministre}}, from {{etyl|la|en}} {{m|la|minister||an attendant, servant, assistant, a priest's assistant or other under official}}, from {{m|la|minor||less}} + {{m|la|-ter}}; see [[minor]].

